---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Terms of Service – TrendSeek" description="Terms of Service for TrendSeek." />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="container legal-page">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: March 4, 2026</p>

      <p>By accessing and using <strong>TrendSeek</strong> ("the Website"), you agree to the following terms and conditions.</p>

      <h2>1. Content</h2>
      <p>All content on TrendSeek is provided for <strong>informational and educational purposes only</strong>. We make every effort to ensure accuracy, but we do not guarantee the completeness, reliability, or timeliness of any information published.</p>
      <p>Articles may cover topics including finance, technology, science, and economy. <strong>Nothing on this website constitutes financial, investment, legal, or medical advice.</strong> Always consult a qualified professional before making decisions based on information found here.</p>

      <h2>2. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All original content, including articles, images, and design elements, is owned by TrendSeek and protected by copyright laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or republish content without prior written permission.</p>

      <h2>3. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or privacy practices of external sites.</p>

      <h2>4. Advertising</h2>
